&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td style=&quot;height: 20px;&quot; width=&quot;231&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An individual who is clear on their personal objectives and plans accordingly&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
