&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td style=&quot;height: 41px;&quot; width=&quot;231&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Someone who can pay attention, interact and support a conversation, probing for further information when required&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
